{"tid":1215944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想同橋上嘅巴絲講幾句野","createTime":"2019-06-13T08:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:45:43.000Z","uid":148034,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fdea9c41d54788187caa20033c2dcf116040d19d","tid":1215944,"uid":148034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:38:48.000Z","msg":"首先聲明我尊重每個人嘅決定<br />\n相信留係橋上嘅大家有自己嘅包伏，苦衷<br />\n但既然你地黎得現場就絕對有心支持樓下嘅義士<br />\n係橋下其中一個問題係視野同通信<br />\n希望橋上嘅巴絲可以主動提供幫助做哨兵<br />\n用大聲公通告情況e.g.邊個位需要咩物資<br />\n有能力嘅就幫手去附近買物資再拋落黎<br />\n畢竟橋上嘅戒備一定比較少<br />\n最後提提大家記得帶翻個口罩保障自己<br />\n香港加油"},{"pid":"f21759710ee0e09412883df2c80442f15dbb1fa5","tid":1215944,"uid":83025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"or 冇野做果陣幫手傳遞資訊，記得fact check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb92f170794ef485070a3ab8f972dcbe7d94dd3c","tid":1215944,"uid":148034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f21759710ee0e09412883df2c80442f15dbb1fa5","tid":1215944,"uid":83025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"or 冇野做果陣幫手傳遞資訊，記得fact check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:45:43.000Z","msg":"樓下啲訊號差到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}